playstore_details.title: Cryptra - Cryptocurrency Tracker for Bittrex
playstore_details.description:
If you have an account in Bittrex Exchange and want to easily keep track of you portfolio with just two clicks instead of going to the website, this is an app for you.
• Attractive user interface
•Just 2 clicks portfolio tracking
• No login required

- Developed By Lokesh , Karan , Akash in the Mobile Computing course offered by Prof. Vinayak Naik in 2018 at IIT Bombay.
playstore_details.summary: An App to track your crypto portfolio linked to Bittrex exchange.
